    <author initials="R." surname="Bush" fullname="Randy Bush"/>
    <date day="14" month="May" year="2012"/>
    <abstract>
      <t>   BGPsec-speaking routers must be provisioned with private keys and the
   corresponding public key must be published in the global Resource
   PKI.  This document describes two ways of doing so, router-driven and
   operator-driven.

	 </t>
